It also involves natural language processing (cs.CL) as the captions are generated using language models. The use of external sources of information suggests the involvement of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) techniques. Finally, the paper also involves information retrieval (cs.IR) as it deals with integrating external sources of information into the captioning process.
